  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 230&deg;C/ 210&deg;C (fan)/ 450&deg;F/ Gas 8</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-size pieces and add to a baking tray</p>\r\n<p>Drizzle with<strong> vegetable oil</strong>, the <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can&rsquo;t handle the heat? Go easy!) and a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Oven roast for 25-30 min or until crispy</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, zest and juice the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>&nbsp;into a <strong>baking dish</strong> large enough to fit the chicken</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks, and add it to the dish</p>\r\n<p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> and plenty of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix well and set aside</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p>\r\n<p>Season both sides with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> whilst cooking</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>mayonnaise</strong> and <strong>chipotle paste</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season lightly with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>- this is your <strong>chipotle mayonnaise</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix well and set aside for serving</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-4-x700.jpg",
