          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once golden, transfer the pan-fried <strong>chicken</strong> to the <strong>baking&nbsp;dish</strong> and coat the chicken in the mixture</p>\r\n<p>Tip: use tongs for better control</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/499.step-5-x400.jpg",
