      "instruction": "<p>Serve the chicken over a bed of lettuce with the warm coriander lime dressing spooned over</p>\r\n<p>Add the spicy potatoes to the side with the chipotle mayonnaise drizzled over</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
